For a bunch of icons I've made myself, click here: http://tinyurl.com/emicons
Feel free to use them.

To use this style, simply replace "INSERTIMAGEURLHERE" with an image url of your choice. The site generally uses 20x20 pixel transparent .pngs.
From top to bottom, you can replace TROPHIES, WHISPER BUBBLE, SUN, NOOSE, NO REVEAL, SCORE, KARMA, LIVES, VILLAGE, GRAVEYARD, DAY PHASE, NIGHT PHASE, and ROLE icons.

NOTE: TO CHANGE AN ICON, YOU MUST REMOVE THE /* and */ BEFORE AND AFTER THE ICON YOU WANT TO CHANGE. FOR EXAMPLE, IF THE CODE LOOKS LIKE THIS AND YOU WANT TO CHANGE SCOUT:

*/ /*
.role-scout {
background: transparent url('INSERTIMAGEURLHERE') no-repeat scroll left top !important;
}
*/ /*

CHANGE IT TO THIS:

*/
.role-scout {
background: transparent url('INSERTIMAGEURLHERE') no-repeat scroll left top !important;
}
